      HANDLER @ ?DUP IF              \ and there's a frame to pop
         RP!                         \ set return stack to frame
         R>RESTORE-INPUT             \ restore input source
         R> HANDLER !                \ set pointer to next frame
         R> SWAP >R                  \ keep exception number
         SP!                         \ restore data stack
